You gain a 1st-level spell slot and a 2nd-level spell slot from your archetype's magical tradition. 

If you have a spell repertoire, you can select one spell from your repertoire as a signature spell. 

At 10th level, you replace your 1st-level spell slot with a 3rd-level spell slot.
